4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Data Science & Machine Learning course that equips students with essential skills to start a career as a data scientist. Over 16 weeks, learners will attend three classes weekly, with a maximum of 12 students per class. The curriculum covers Python, SQL, statistics, and data visualization tools like Looker while delving into algorithms and machine learning models. Classes are available in English and Spanish, catering to diverse learners. No prior experience is required, and upon completion, graduates receive a recognized certificate. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop